{"title_page": "Romeo (2020 film)", "text_new": "{{short description|2020 romantic drama film directed by Ali Khan}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = November 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date = November 2019}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Romeo\n| image          = \n| alt            = \n| caption        = \n| director       = [[Ali Khan (director)|Ali Khan]]\n| producer       = Raj Sharma<br>Tussar<br>[[Jyoti Taygi]]<br>[[Eros International]]\n| writer         = [[Ali Khan (director)|Ali Khan]]\n| story          = \n| starring       = Vicky Kadian<br>Kajal Sharma<br>[[Pankaj Tripathi]]<br>[[Shriya Pilgaonkar]]\n| music          = \n| cinematography = [[Ravi K. Chandran]]\n| editing        = \n| studio         = Good Film\n| distributor    = [[Eros International]]\n| released       = {{Film date|df=yes|2020|6|18|India}}\n| country        = [[India]]\n| language       = [[Hindi]]\n| budget         = <!--Must be attributed to a reliable published source with an established reputation for fact-checking. No blogs, no IMDb.-->\n| gross          = <!--Must be attributed to a reliable published source with an established reputation for fact-checking. No blogs, no IMDb.-->\n| based on       = \n}}\n'''''Romeo''''' is an upcoming Indian [[Hindi]]-language [[romantic drama]] film directed by [[Ali Khan (director)|Ali Khan]] and produced by Raj Sharma under the banner Good Film. The film features Vicky Kadian and Kajal Sharma in the lead roles.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pagalparrot.com/vicky-kadian-starrer-romeo-to-release-in-march-2020/|title=Vicky Kadian Starrer Romeo to release in March 2020|date=2019-10-18|website=PagalParrot|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hindi.pardaphash.com/actor-vicky-kadian-upcoming-movie-romeo|title=\u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0936\u0941\u0930\u0942 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u0940 \u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e \u2018Romeo\u2019 \u0915\u0940 \u0936\u0942\u091f\u093f\u0902\u0917, \u0907\u0938 \u092d\u0942\u092e\u09